================================================================================
SCOPE
================================================================================
This repository contains reusable, self-contained tooling (zero runtime deps),
plus its schema/, docs/ and examples/. The executable tools are:
  - sbom.mjs            — CycloneDX-lite SBOM generator (per-file SHA-256; --verify)
  - make_bundle.mjs     — deterministic evidence-bundle manifest builder
  - verify_bundle.mjs   — independent bundle verifier (organ / third party)
  - attest-verify.mjs   — attestation verifier (never signs; UNSIGNED_DRAFT/HALT_FOR_ACK)
  - dep-provenance.mjs  — jurisdiction_class per component (agents-not-people; no person scoring)
  - procurement-check.mjs — procurement readiness checklist
  - sbom-expose.mjs     — SBOM exposure/diff helper

The proprietary K0NSULT orchestration engine (k0nsult.cloud) is NOT part of this
repository and is never open-sourced. These generators operate on any directory
you point them at (`--root <path>`); they carry no engine code, no data, no keys.
The ipIII evidence-attestation module is a COMMERCIAL product currently for sale;
it is NOT open-sourced and NOT covered by the Apache-2.0 grant here (open-source
only conditionally, if unsold — operator Human Override).
LICENSE (Apache-2.0) covers the entire repository; this list is descriptive, not
a limitation of scope.

================================================================================
DOCTRINE (invariant)
================================================================================
  - claim <= proof (evidence-first; the bundle is a DRAFT until an operator signs it)
  - Human Override Always (signing is a human action, off-tool)
  - No Password Custody — these tools never generate, store, or request a private key
